119
00:09:05,559 --> 00:09:07,399
Yu, why the hurry to dress?

120
00:09:08,000 --> 00:09:09,399
You rarely visit my palace.

121
00:09:10,759 --> 00:09:12,399
Don't you want to stay a little longer?

122
00:09:14,879 --> 00:09:17,279
I've done what you asked.

123
00:09:18,240 --> 00:09:18,720
From now on,

124
00:09:19,679 --> 00:09:21,080
don't meddle in palace affairs.

125
00:09:35,960 --> 00:09:36,840
Yu,

126
00:09:37,480 --> 00:09:39,159
are you saying

127
00:09:39,679 --> 00:09:41,440
last night, we truly...

128
00:09:46,159 --> 00:09:46,600
You.

129
00:09:47,159 --> 00:09:48,159
What are you doing there?

130
00:09:48,559 --> 00:09:49,919
These words aren't for your ears.

131
00:09:50,519 --> 00:09:52,679
What do you know about love
between a man and a woman?

